- Version 4.1.1,  Revision 13979,  Hash 53da1aa. [Davide Sangalli]

  MODIFIED *  .gitattributes config/configure.ac configure include/version.inc sbin/yambo_versions_update.tcsh

  NEW *  config/version.m4

  Changes:
  - [configure] yambo_version is now written in config/version.m4 and not in configure.ac
                Accordingly it is the config/version.m4 file which is protected on merge and
                not anymore the config/configure.ac
                In case errors are done in merging the configure (which is still protected) it is suffiecient
                to run autoconf to have the proper configure

  Patch sent by:  Davide Sangalli <davide.sangalli@gmail.com>

- Version 4.1.f,  Revision 13976,  Hash 1433dfa. [marini]

  MODIFIED *  config/configure.ac configure driver/ypp_driver.F include/version.inc lib/perl/ydb/create_new_run.pm lib/perl/ydb/database.pm lib/perl/ydb/functions.pm lib/perl/ydb/load_db.pm lib/perl/ydb/objects_IO.pm lib/perl/ydb/print_the_run.pm lib/perl/ydb/remove_run.pm qp/XCo_local.F ypp/init/INIT_ypp.F ypp/symmetries/symmetries_driver.F

  NEW *

  RENAMED *  sbin/ydb.pl -> sbin/ydb.pl.in

  Changes:
  -  Working on ydb.pl

  Patch sent by:  marini <andrea.marini@cnr.it>

