- Version 4.1.0,  Revision 13891,  Hash bcf06a9. [marini]

  MODIFIED *  config/configure.ac configure include/version.inc bse/K_inversion_do_it_full.F bse/K_inversion_driver.F bse/K_inversion_engine.F bse/K_solvers.F interface/INIT.F interface/INIT_load.F linear_algebra/LINEAR_ALGEBRA_driver.F modules/SET_defaults.F modules/mod_SLK.F modules/mod_linear_algebra.F modules/mod_parallel.F parallel/PARALLEL_assign_LA_COMMs.F parallel/PARALLEL_global_indexes.F pol_function/X_s.F

  Additions:
  - Added specific INV/DIAGO cpu's in INIT

  Changes:
  - SLK messages moved from the LA driver to the PARALLEL LA comms initialization.
  - PARALLEL LA comms initialization for BS solvers moved out of global index to handle differently INV and DIAGO.
  - Removed unused variables.

  Patch sent by:  marini <andrea.marini@cnr.it>

