  -

  Additions:
  -

  Changes:
  - README.git: info for creating a tag inserted

  Patch sent by:  Davide Sangalli <davide.sangalli@gmail.com>

- Default of ChiLinAlgMod changed to "lin_sys" (always faster than
  inversion) [Andrea Ferretti]

- X_s: inversion + multiplication now uses parallel linear algebra for
  both operations. [Andrea Ferretti]

- Dual setup (inv & diago) for parallel linear algebra removed. related
  input vars renamed. [Andrea Ferretti]

- Initialization of parallel linear algebra moved upstream wrt
  LINAR_ALGEBRA_driver.F . Deadlock in X_s with q-pools removed (a check
  ensured serial algebra, removed) [Andrea Ferretti]

- Eval_G_minus_G made MPI parallel in selected calls. [Andrea Ferretti]

- Function eval_G_minus_G equipped with an optional  MPI_comm in input
  and added to interfaces. [Andrea Ferretti]

- Merge branch 'master' into stabilize-yambo-sc. [marini]

