  to verify the effective correcteness of the fix. [Andrea Marini]

  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/branches/devel-andrea@5263 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

