  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@1489 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.5. [Claudio Attaccalite]

  *  wf_and_fft/WF_load.F pol_function/.objects pol_function/Dipole_driver.F pol_function/Dipole_transverse.F pol_function/Dipole_rotate.F setup/setup.F setup/QP_state_table_setup.F interface/init_load.F interface/init.F sc/SC_WF_and_dipole_dimensions.F sc/SC_start_and_restart.F sc/SC_driver.F sc/.objects sc/SC_History.F sc/SC_update_dipoles.F io/variables_SC.F io/io_SC_components.F modules/mod_wave_func.F modules/std_presets.F modules/mod_SC.F

