  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@1251 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.5. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc int_modules/mod_com2y.F p2y/p2y_i.F config/configure.ac xc_functionals/el_density.F wf_and_fft/fft_setup.F wf_and_fft/scatter_Bamp.F setup/setup.F sc/OEP_driver.F sc/OEP_iterative.F sc/OEP_ApplySigmaX.F sc/OEP_Weighted_Density.F sc/OEP_app_inversion.F sc/OEP_ApplySigmaCSX.F sc/OEP_Hole.F tddft/tddft_alda_r_space.F io/ioDB1.F modules/mod_wave_func.F modules/mod_FFT.F modules/mod_D_lattice.F ypp/excitons_non_collinear.F ypp/excitons_driver.F ypp/RT_fix_symmetries.F

  Changes:
  - fft_rot_r now is constructed for all symmetries only from the spatial part of each symmetry.
    I.e. if del_sop include the t-rev fft_rot_r is constructed from -dl_sop

  - spin_orbit logical removed from ioDB1.F and substituted by logical mag_sym
    the logical spin_orbit is still used in a2y

  Patch sent by: Davide


