  - [configure] Fixed procedures to identify external BLAS/LAPACK libraries
  - [configure] Starting the rewriting of the SCALAPACK support

  Additions:
  - Starting adding GGA/BLYP and hybrid xc functionals support
  - [YPP] Added interface to the Wannier90 code

  Changes:
  - [GPL] Removed barrier to electronic temperature

