- Version 3.2.4. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc config/configure.ac real_time/RT_ELPH_Kernel.F real_time/RT_ELPH_Kernel.F_ORI real_time/RT_generalized_KBA.F real_time/RT_ELPH_initialize.F real_time/RT_generalized_KBA.F_ORI io/ioELPH.F modules/mod_real_time.F ypp/electrons_driver.F

  Bugs:
  - [RT] Electron-phonon dynamics was causing the decay of all electronic levels. This was due to an incorrect
         nesting of the band indexes in the ELPH kernel.

  Additions:
  - [RT] Analytic fit of the phonon bands of bulk hbn

  Changes:
  - [RT] Implmentation of time integration removed. The version in rev. 969 (with a smal patch) is
    the only one working with a diagonal-only interaction. It was useless to keep the time integration
    as it is terribly slow.

  Patch sent by: Andrea


