  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@900 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.4. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc e2y/e2y_db1.F e2y/e2y_i.F e2y/e2y_kb_pp.F int_modules/mod_com2y.F p2y/numrec_polcof.F p2y/qexml_v4.0.F p2y/pw_atoms_module.F p2y/numrec_module.F p2y/pw_struct_module.F p2y/p2y_db1.F p2y/numrec_ddpoly.F p2y/p2y_wf.F p2y/mod_p2y.F p2y/Vnl_driver.F p2y/pw_pseudo_module.F p2y/num_interpolation_module.F p2y/pw_basis_module.F p2y/mod_pw_data.F p2y/mod_numerical.F p2y/numrec_polint.F p2y/numrec_locate.F p2y/numrec_kinds.F p2y/p2y_i.F p2y/.objects p2y/pw_pseudovelocity_module.F p2y/pw_wfc_module.F a2y/a2y_db1.F a2y/a2y_i.F a2y/a2y_wf.F c2y/c2y_i.F config/Makefile.in config/configure.ac pol_function/Dipole_kb_pp_comp.F pol_function/Dipole_transverse.F io/io_Vnl.F io/ioKB_PP.F io/.objects modules/mod_pseudo.F modules/std_presets.F ypp/RT_fix_symmetries.F driver/p2y.h

  ***** MAJOR UPDATE: [r,Vnl] support added in p2y ******

  Thanks to Conor. Andrea did only the final mergering and added the parallel support.

  Additions:
  - [A2Y] Added support to pseudopotential projectors.
    Davide will shortly extend the non-local commutator to the relativistic case.
    * pp_n_l_comp_max -> pp_n_l_times_proj_max
    * Added a new table (pp_table)

  - Added PARALLEL support to p2y. It can now run in parallel.

  - [P2Y] Added **SEVERAL** PW-based routines to import the commutator of the non-local pseudo.
    Some cleaning still todo. In many cases the License header is missing.

  - A new core database: (n)s.Vnl

  - A new option for p2y (-c)

  Changes:
  - Interfaces do not call section at the beginning. Instead a simple msg is used.
  - The old flag of p2y (-g, Force use of all available RL vectors) now changed so
    to load a certain number of G-vectors.

  Patch sent by: Andrea, Davide & Conor


