  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@840 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.4. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc config/configure.ac ypp/ypp_init.F ypp/RT_databases.F ypp/RT_X_effective.F ypp/RT_driver.F ypp/RT_init_X_one.F ypp/mod_YPP.F ypp/RT_paths.F ypp/ypp_init_load.F ypp/RT_X_one.F ypp/.objects

  Additions:
  - [YPP_RT] RT_driver changed in order to avoid DB loading at the beginning
  - [YPP_RT] Databases paths are now searched in RT_paths. This routine returns
    the number of Pumps and Probes found. On this basis RT_driver decides what to do.
  - [YPP_RT] Added Kwywords in input file: ProbeKey PumpKey

  Now ypp_rt works (ss before) with any hermitian single probe or with a pump (any) plus several resonant probes.
  I will add shortly the possibility of using a single pump plus a single probe (pulse-like).

  Patch sent by: Andrea


