- Version 3.2.4. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc config/configure.ac qp/QP_report_and_write.F parser/mod_itm.F pol_function/Dipole_driver.F pol_function/Dipole_transverse.F interface/init_load.F interface/init.F real_time/RT_Ext_fields.F real_time/RT_apply_field.F real_time/RT_Energy.F real_time/RT_Collision.F real_time/RT_driver.F real_time/RT_current_AND_polarization.F real_time/RT_initialize.F real_time/RT_Ext_Current.F real_time/RT_propagate_vecpot.F real_time/RT_qp_analyze.F real_time/RT_update_G_reference.F real_time/RT_init_two_levels.F real_time/RT_propagate_fields.F real_time/RT_databases_IO.F real_time/.objects real_time/RT_Integrator.F real_time/RT_start_and_restart.F real_time/RT_init_vecpot.F real_time/RT_two_levels.F real_time/RT_average_operator.F io/variables_SC.F io/io_SC_components.F modules/mod_real_time.F modules/mod_units.F modules/mod_fields.F modules/std_presets.F ypp/ypp_init.F ypp/RT_databases.F ypp/RT_driver.F ypp/RT_init_X_one.F ypp/Fourier_Transform.F ypp/mod_YPP.F ypp/ypp_init_load.F + ypp/RT_X_two.F ypp/RT_X_one.F ypp/RT_damp_it.F ypp/.objects

  *** MAJOR [_RT] Version UPDATE: moved to 3.2.4 ***

  Bugs:
  - [RT] DIP_P and DIP_iR have transposed band indexes. This was not
    taken in account in RT. So bugs were introduced in RT_apply_field.F and
    RT_current_AND_polarization. RT_average_operator changed accordingly adding a
    flag to perform the transpose.

  Additions:
  - [RT] Several new variables and subroutine have been added.

  Changes:
  - [RT] RT_driver cleaned and re-organized
  - [RT] External fields routines and module revised. Now the external field
    is defined in RT_Ext_Fields and propagated in RT_propagate_fields. The propagation, however,
    is actually done only if the induced current is considered.
  - [YPP_RT] RT_databases.F cleaned.
  - [YPP_RT] Calls to FT unified in RT_1D_Fourier_Transform.F

  Patch sent by: Andrea


  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@743 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

