  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@666 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.2. [Andrea Marini]

  *  trunk/configure trunk/include/version.inc trunk/p2y/.objects trunk/config/Makefile.in trunk/config/Makefile.in_gpl trunk/config/configure.ac trunk/real_time/RT_two_levels.F trunk/driver/driver.c trunk/sbin/yamboo.pl branches/gpl/configure branches/gpl/include/version.inc branches/gpl/config/configure.ac branches/gpl/setup/G_shells_finder.F branches/gpl/interface/init_load.F branches/gpl/interface/init.F branches/gpl/io/variables_BS.F branches/gpl/io/ioQP.F branches/gpl/modules/mod_drivers.F branches/gpl/modules/mod_global_XC.F branches/gpl/bse/K_Haydock.F branches/gpl/bse/K_BSmat_by_V.F

  *** WARNING *** Commit message of revision 661 is wrong (My mistake :(, Andrea)

  Additions:
  - [GPL branch]: *** BSE/TDDFT beyond the TDA ***
    It is now possible to calculate TDDFT and BSE response functions beyond the
    Tamm-Dancoff approximation. The antiresonant and coupling blocks of the
    Hamiltonians can be computed.
    The final Dyson equation is, then. solved using diagonalization or the
    quasi-Hermitian Haydock algorithm proposed in Nano Letters, 9, 2820 (2009)
  - AUGER project opened.

  Patch sent by: The Team


  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@662 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.2. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc config/configure.ac interface/init_load.F interface/init.F setup/G_shells_finder.F real_time/RT_two_levels.F sc/XC_switch.F sc/OEP_kli_iterative.F sc/OEP_driver.F sc/OEP_exact_inversion.F sc/SC_add_XC.F sc/V_oep.F sc/SC_start_and_restart.F sc/OEP_kli_inversion.F sc/.objects sc/OEP_exact_iterative.F sc/OEP_Hole.F io/variables_BS.F io/ioQP.F modules/mod_drivers.F modules/std_presets.F modules/mod_SC.F modules/mod_global_XC.F bse/K_Haydock.F bse/K_BSmat_by_V.F bse/K_BSload.F

  Bugs:
  - Kinetic energy cutoff wrongly defined (Claudio)
  - [RT] compiling with gfortran (Claudio)

  Additions:
  - [SC] Slater potential for the only X case (tested only for few cases, more/rigorous tests needed)
  - [SC] Kli potential for the only X case both with iterative and standard solution (from few tests iterative version seems to work) (Myrta)
  - [SC] Iterative solution of OEP equation only X (does not work yet) (Myrta)
  - [SC] "Driver" for managing all OEP options/subroutines   (Myrta)

  Changes:
  - Removed NONGPL barriers for BSE with Coupling (Myrta)
  - [SC] V_oep changed to sc/OEP_exact_inversion.F to conform to new subroutines naming (Myrta)
  - [SC] changes in interfaces/modules/sc routines to introduce new OEP options/drivers (Myrta)

  Patch sent by: Myrta & Claudio


