  Bugs:
  - In init_load due to a too long variable description

  Additions:
  - New array for <n|p|n'>: DIP_P
  - RT_ouput to write real-time and energy resolved A,P,J ... eps, eels
  - Added polarization in io_SC_components

  Changes:
  - ioOSTNTS renamed in io_DIPOLES (DB name changed as well)
  - Removed back-compatibility of OSTENTS databases
  - **GLOBAL** renaming of:
     DIP_iq_dot_r -> DIP_q_dot_iR
     DIP_iR_or_P  -> DIP_iR
  - Removed dependence on gauge of Dipole_transverse. Now DIP_iR is filled with <iR> while
    Dipole_driver fills DIP_P at the occurrence
  - Changed the way output files are written by RT_driver in order to be compatible with ypp_rt
  - RT_current_AND_polarization now calculated current AND polarization at the same time
  - **GLOBAL** restyling of ypp_rt. Old RT_spectrum splitted in RT_databases.F, RT_driver.F and
    RT_optics.F. Note that RT_optics has been deeply revised in order to use Polarization instead
    of current to evaluate optical properties

  Patch sent by: Andrea


