   -[SC] Bug in variables_SC.F, the variable CHECK_ was not initialized, set to .not.l_NSC_shot
   -[SC] Bug in SC_History.F, when there are too many k-points the string to print
         is larger than lchlen (set max kpoints to 6)

  Patch sent by: Claudio


