- Version 3.2.1. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc p2y/mod_p2y.F a2y/a2y_db1.F a2y/elk_db1.F a2y/a2y_i.F a2y/elk_wf.F config/Makefile.in_gpl config/configure.ac xc_functionals/el_current.F xc_functionals/.objects xc_functionals/spin_density.F wf_and_fft/WF_derivative.F wf_and_fft/WF_load.F pol_function/X_os.F interface/init_load.F setup/check_periodic_directions.F real_time/RT_propagate_vecpot.F communicate/fermi_msg.F sc/MAG_common_build_A.F sc/SC_driver.F sc/SC_check_symmetries.F sc/MAG_Hamiltonian.F modules/mod_units.F modules/std_presets.F modules/mod_magnetic.F bse/K.F ypp/ypp_init.F ypp/electrons_current.F ypp/RT_spectrum.F ypp/mod_YPP.F ypp/electrons_position.F ypp/ypp_init_load.F ypp/electrons_driver.F ypp/.objects ypp/electrons_angular_momentum.F driver/ypp.h

  Bugs:
  - RT_spectrum.F: few bugs fixed (Davide)

  Additions:
  - added load_cc() function in mod_magnetic which load x(3,fft_size) the cartesian coordinates
    centered with respect to cell_center(3)=(0,0,0) (Davide)
  - xc_functionals/el_current.F, xc_functionals/.objects, ypp/electrons_current.F :
    evaluate the current_density and its average (Davide)
  - ypp/electrons_position.F :
    evaluate the average position of the electrons (Davide)

  Changes:
  - changed units convention, now the speed_of_light factor is not implicitely
    inside A_magn but is used in the construction of MAG_hamiltonian as it should be (Davide)
  - name average_two_spin_density moved in average_el_mag (Davide)
  - ypp/electrons_angular_momentum.F: added call to load_cc() which is in mod_magnetic (Davide)
  - WF_derivative.F: added check the number of bands before warning that SC_bands have to be derived (Davide)
  - WF_load.F, bse/K.F, pol_function/X_os.F : changes in comments (Davide)
  - sc/SC_check_symmetries.F : higher tolerance for magnetic symmetries (Davide)
  - interface/init_load.F : NonPerDir loaded by default in the input  (Davide)
  - ELK2Y interface updated (Andrea)

  Patch sent by: Andrea, Claudio & Davide


