  *  configure + + tests/load_paths_and_executables.sh.in + tests/setup.sh + + include/version.inc config/report.in config/Makefile.in config/configure.ac doc/tests doc/tests/test_magnetic.sh doc/tests/test_GoWo.sh doc/tests/test_SC.sh xc_functionals/el_magnetization.F qp/XCo_local.F qp/XCo_driver.F qp/XCo_Hartree_Fock.F qp/QP_eval_RHO_RHO.F qp/.objects qp/QP_elph.F qp/QP_ppa_chosex.F qp/QP_store_RHO_RHO_VX.F parser/ps_convert.F wf_and_fft/WF_load.F pol_function/X_os.F pol_function/Dipole_driver.F pol_function/Dipole_transverse.F interface/init_load.F interface/init.F setup/check_periodic_directions.F setup/setup.F communicate/fermi_msg.F io/ioDB1.F io/ioRHO_RHO_VX.F modules/mod_memory.F modules/std_presets.F modules/.objects modules/mod_magnetic.F driver/editor.h.in driver/yambo_driver.F

  *** DEBUG VERSION. NOT FOR PRODUCTION ***

  Bugs:
  - Bugs fixed in order to be able to run HF+RHO I/O standalone.

  Additions:
  - src/qp/QP_eval_RHO_RHO.F. See below.

  Changes:
  - Tests reshaped. Now added to Makefile with automatic path generation via configure.
  - _MAGNETIC replaced as an additional flag to _SC. So to compile yambo_magnetic now
    a -D_MAGNETIC -D_SC is used.
  - I am gradually extracting the RHO_RHO I/O from the original Claudio's routines. The procedures
    will be in a new routine that can be used by _SC as well.

  Patch sent by: Andrea


