  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@496 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.1. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc config/configure.ac xc_functionals/el_magnetization.F qp/XCo_driver.F qp/XCo_Hartree_Fock.F qp_ctl/QP_load_DB.F wf_and_fft/WF_derivative.F wf_and_fft/wf_load.F interface/init_load.F interface/init.F communicate/fermi_msg.F sc/MAG_common_build_A.F sc/SC_driver.F sc/MAG_Hamiltonian.F io/ioRHO_RHO_VX.F modules/mod_wave_func.F modules/mod_oscillators_IO.F modules/std_presets.F modules/mod_magnetic.F bse/K.F ypp/RT_fix_symmetries.F

