  - [MAGNETIC] added average_magnetization variable in mod_magnetic and its computation in el_magnetization.F.
    Then inserted calls to el_mag in SC_driver to report the average_el_mag in SC_driver and fermi_msg.F (Davide)
  - [MAGNETIC] wf_load.F : when an SC_database is found is possible to load a limitated number of k points
               (EXPERIMENTAL) (Davide)
