  Bugs:
  - [SC] Many bugs corrected in Real-Time dynamics (C)

  Additions:
  - [SC] 2nd order Runge-Kutta integrator for Real-Time dynamics (C)
  - [SC] Integration algorithm with or without fast phase factors integration
         (RTNoPhaseInt variable) (C)

  Changes:
  - Input file name set to "(none)" when the file is not found/written (A)
  - Added set_real_printed_length rotuine in STDERR module in order
    to tune on-fly the format of the output/report file for reals (A)
  - ypp/BZ_RIM.F randon generator rewritten (A)


