- Version 3.2.0. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc config/Makefile.in config/acx.m4 config/configure.ac pol_function/X_pre_setup.F pol_function/X_bare_RIM_Gf.F interface/setup.F interface/init_load.F interface/init.F modules/mod_electrons.F modules/std_presets.F bse/K_driver.F driver/driver.c sbin/yamboo.pl

  Bugs:
  - When inv_index < 0 seg fault in BSE with coupling.

  Additions:
