  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@338 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.0. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc config/configure.ac qp/QP_newton.F qp_ctl/mod_QP_CTL.F qp_ctl/QP_apply_fit.F qp_ctl/QP_apply_db.F pol_function/X_em1.F interface/setup.F modules/mod_IO.F bse/K_driver.F

  Bugs:
  - In QP_apply_fit.F the QP energies were erroneously shifted
    to the max/min of the LDA conduction/valence states.
  - The solvers of the BSE were called even if the Kernel
    was only partially evaluated  (BS_columns<NK_IBZ)
  - The XC KIND of an existing QP database was transferred
    to the energy types (in mod_QP_CTL.F) even if the
    database was not actually used.

  Patch sent by: Andrea


  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@337 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.0. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure include/version.inc config/configure.ac xc_functionals/el_density.F xc_functionals/xc_lda_driver.F xc_functionals/el_magnetization.F qp/DFT_Vxc.F qp_ctl/mod_QP_CTL.F interface/init_load.F communicate/report_energies.F communicate/fermi_msg.F modules/mod_QP.F ypp/ypp_init.F ypp/plot_xcrysden.F ypp/mod_YPP.F ypp/plot_gnuplot.F ypp/plot_driver.F ypp/ypp_init_load.F driver/ypp.h

  Bugs:
  - Wrong spin loop in el_density. Bug introduced in rev. 277. Only
    spin up density calculated.
  - Erroneous assignment of spin up/down to components 1 and 2
    of energy, occupation ... arrays.

  Additions:
  - Ypp can plot spin resolved wavefunctions and densities
    (only spin-polarized case supported)

  Patch sent by: Andrea


