  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@335 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.2.0. [Andrea Marini]

  *  trunk/configure trunk/include/version.inc trunk/config/acx_cpp.m4 trunk/config/configure.ac trunk/pol_function/O_driver.F trunk/bse/K_dump_to_o_file.F trunk/sbin/yamboo.pl branches/gpl/configure branches/gpl/include/version.inc branches/gpl/config/report.in branches/gpl/config/Makefile.in branches/gpl/config/acx_report.m4 branches/gpl/config/acx.m4 branches/gpl/config/acx_mpi.m4 branches/gpl/config/netcdf_f90.m4 branches/gpl/config/configure.ac branches/gpl/config/acx_lapack.m4 branches/gpl/config/setup.in branches/gpl/qp_ctl/QP_apply_stretch.F branches/gpl/qp_ctl/mod_QP_CTL.F branches/gpl/qp_ctl/QP_apply_done.F branches/gpl/parser/mod_itm.F branches/gpl/pol_function/X_os.F branches/gpl/pol_function/O_driver.F branches/gpl/interface/init_load.F branches/gpl/interface/init.F branches/gpl/modules/mod_electrons.F branches/gpl/modules/std_presets.F branches/gpl/modules/mod_QP.F branches/gpl/bse/K_dump_to_o_file.F branches/gpl/bse/K.F branches/gpl/ypp/ypp_init.F branches/gpl/ypp/ypp_init_load.F branches/gpl/driver/ypp.h branches/gpl/sbin/make_makefile.sh.in

  Bugs:
  - [TRUNK] When using a Coulomb cutoff AND a non-resonant
    BSE the polarizability was not correctly defined.

  Additions:
  - Added check for dlaran when using external lapack lib.
    In case dlaran is missing an additional lib (lib/local)
    is compiled and linked.
  - Added check for C/Fortran precompiler in configure.
  - Changed -with--netcdf with --with-netcdf-include AND
    --with-netcdf-lib. Both must be passed to configure to
    activate NETCDF support.
  - Added V_testing verbosity level.
  - X_os.F restiled to be processed by yamboo.pl.
  - Verbosity to ypp.

  Changes:
  - [TRUNK] Removed X_os from "special" treatment in yamboo.pl
  - [TRUNK] Added spin support to all routines in qp_ctl.
            As consequence all related types have been
            resized. Also init_load.F and init.F have been changed
            accordingly.


  Patch sent by: Andrea


