- Version 3.1.2. [Andrea Marini]

  *  config/acx.m4 wf_and_fft/fft_setup.F interface/init.F coulomb/.objects_gpl coulomb/col_driver.F io/ioBSS_diago.F modules/mod_wave_func.F modules/std_presets.F modules/mod_FFT.F ypp/exc_properties.F ypp/exc_wf_sort_and_report.F ypp/exc_collinear_spin.F ypp/mod_YPP.F ypp/exc_non_collinear_spin.F ypp/ypp_i.F

  Additions:
  - Added fft_multiplier in mod_FFT to allow for multiplication
    of FFT grid. Still not passed to the input file.
  - RIM and CUTOFF added to GPL version
  - YPP is now able to plot excitonic/TDALDA wfs in the case
    where the coupling part of the Hamiltonian is used.

  Changes:
  - Path to cpp in acx.m4

