  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@224 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.1.0. [Andrea Marini]

  SELF project ends today :( replaced by the
  glorious (?) YAMBO 3.1.0 project.

  I have just registered the www.yambo-code.org and
  created the mail address yambo@yambo-code.org.

  At the moment www.yambo-code.org is forwarded to the SELF
  web-page. I will change it today.

  Regarding the names:

  self -> yambo
  *2s (a2s, p2s ...) -> *2y (a2y, p2y ....)
  spp -> ypp

  Patch sent by: Andrea


