- Version 3.0.16. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure spp/ioDB1_ver_2.F spp/exc_properties.F spp/mod_SPP.F spp/spp_i.F spp/.objects spp/spp_init_load.F spp/spp_init.F spp/.objects_gpl spp/exc_wf_xcrysden.F include/version.inc p2s/p2s_i.F p2s/mod_p2s.F a2s/a2s_i.F e2s/e2s_i.F f2s/FHI96SPIN-src f2s/FHI96SPIN-main.f f2s/FHI96SPIN-wr_wvf_n_cell.f f2s/f2s_i.F f2s/.objects_gpl f2s/README config/Makefile.in config/Makefile.in_gpl config/configure.ac + xc_functionals/.objects xc_functionals/xc_lda_driver.F xc_functionals/README qp/QP_driver.F qp/DFT_Vxc.F qp/QP_newton.F + + qp/.objects qp/.objects_gpl qp/QP_ppa_chosex.F acfdt/.objects_gpl qp_ctl/mod_QP_CTL.F qp_ctl/QP_apply_stretch.F qp_ctl/.objects_gpl qp_ctl/QP_apply_fit.F qp_ctl/QP_apply_db.F ras/.objects_gpl common/pol_fit.F common/QP_state_table_setup.F common/bracket.F common/secant.F common/.objects common/.objects_gpl common/rand_identifier.F common/fermi_level.F parser/mod_itm.F wf_and_fft/wf_load.F wf_and_fft/el_density.F wf_and_fft/.objects wf_and_fft/scatter_Bamp.F wf_and_fft/.objects_gpl wf_and_fft/scatter_Gamp.F pol_function/X_O_transverse.F pol_function/X_eh_setup.F pol_function/X_os.F pol_function/X_bare_RIM_Gf.F pol_function/.objects_gpl pol_function/X_O_strengths.F pol_function/X_s.F interface/init_load.F interface/init.F interface/barriers.F coulomb/.objects_gpl coulomb/col_driver.F ras_reels_mods/reels_presets.F ras_reels_mods/.objects_gpl ras_reels_mods/mod_eels_integration.F communicate/section.F communicate/job_setup.F tddft/tddft_do_X_W_typs.F tddft/.objects_gpl sc/.objects_gpl io/ioBS_Fxc.F io/ioDB1.F io/ioBSS_invert.F io/ioQP.F io/ioRIM.F io/io_header.F io/ioCOL_CUT.F io/ioELPH.F io/ioBSS_Haydock.F io/ioE_RIM.F io/.objects_gpl modules/mod_electrons.F modules/mod_logo.F modules/mod_BS.F modules/mod_functions.F modules/mod_drivers.F modules/std_presets.F modules/mod_IO.F modules/mod_com.F modules/.objects bse/K_Haydock.F bse/Kernel_by_V.F bse/K_driver.F bse/K_eps_interpolate.F bse/K_solvers.F bse/K_scattering_cpl.F bse/K_scattering.F bse/.objects bse/.objects_gpl bse/K_eh_setup.F bse/K.F reels/.objects_gpl ChangeLog driver/self.h driver/self.h_gpl driver/self_driver.F driver/spp.h_gpl driver/driver.c

  Bugs:
  - In ioQP. Recently added gloabl_XC kinds casued a I/O
    error in db.QP older than 3.0.15. Fixed.

  Additions:
  - GPL Tags. _gpl .objects, Makefile
  - mod_logo: it chooses a random yambo logo
  - barriers routine to avoid  the use of simultaneous
    (possibly dangerous) runlevels

  Changes:
  - Removed self2self support in spp.
  - runlevel_is_on logical function in mod_itm to replace rstatus integers
    to define an active runlevel
  - Removed rand_identifier, replaced by pickup_a_random in mod_logo
  - Removed FHI96SPIN-src/ (f2s as well ?)
  - module QP_CTL renamed in QP_CTL_m, QP_fit_ctl in QP_ctl_t
  - _CPL project merged in the core. Coupling support in BSE
    now active.
  - In K.F the I/O of epsm1/PP. Now with only -o b option
    the db.em1s ONLY is used. To read the dp.pp a -p p option
    must be used in the command line.

- Version 3.0.16. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure spp/spp_i.F spp/spp_init.F include/version.inc p2s/p2s_i.F a2s/a2s_i.F e2s/e2s_i.F f2s/f2s_i.F config/configure.ac qp/QP_XX_Vxc.F ras/X_O_strengths_cut.F ras/X_O_longitudinal_cut.F parser/mod_itm.F pol_function/X_O_longitudinal.F interface/init_load.F interface/init.F communicate/run_summary.F communicate/.objects communicate/job_setup.F sc/SC_mute.F io/ioDB1_reload.F modules/mod_memory.F modules/mod_timing.F modules/std_presets.F modules/mod_par_proc.F modules/mod_IO.F modules/mod_com.F bse/Kernel_by_V.F driver/self.h driver/self_driver.F driver/spp.h driver/driver.c

  Additions:
  - "-C" argument of c_driver to define a path for report files
  - com_path to define a path for report and output files
  - Support for distributed calculations on clusters. This
    option is activated only when ncpu>1 and core_IO_path/=more_IO_path
  - routine  check_for_a_redundant_IO in mod_par_proc.F

  Changes:
  - master_cpu replaces master_node
  - core_IO_path replaces in_path
  - more_IO_path replaces out_path
  - Verbosity is now incremental. Higher is the value of the -V
    option more variables are showed.
  - job_setup replaces run_summary

  Patch sent by: Andrea


  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@219 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.0.15. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure spp/ioX_ver_2.F spp/ioWF_ver_2.F spp/spp_i.F spp/ioKB_PP_ver_2.F spp/.objects spp/self2self.F include/version.inc config/Makefile.in config/acx.m4 config/configure.ac config/setup.in qp/DFT_Vxc.F qp/QP_XX_Vxc.F qp/QP_ppa_chosex.F common/QP_state_table_setup.F wf_and_fft/wf_load.F wf_and_fft/.objects wf_and_fft/WF_rotate.F interface/init.F sc/SC_driver.F io/io_elemental.F io/ioX.F io/io_SC_components.F io/load_SC_components.F modules/mod_wave_func.F modules/std_presets.F modules/mod_SC.F bse/K.F driver/spp.h sbin/self_save.sh.in sbin/make_makefile.sh.in sbin/objects_debug.sh sbin/objects_debug.sh.in

