  - DFT_Vxc can now read SC potentials. Now it is possible to perform
    EXX+GW calculations.
  - QP_ppa_chosex now stops if incomplete em1s/pp DB is found
  - Added @SHELL@ statement in .sh scripts

  Changes:
  - Removed self2self (ver. 2 database convertor) in spp
  - Removed self_save script
  - Removed check of TCSH, MYECHO and AWK in configure
  - WF_rotate moved out of module and changed in order to
    reduce arrau duplication
  - In SC run created ad-hoc variables (see init.F)


