  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@217 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.0.15. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure spp/exc_properties.F spp/exc_non_collinear_spin.F spp/.objects include/version.inc int_modules/mod_interfaces.F config/configure.ac qp/DFT_Vxc.F qp/QP_XX_Vxc.F qp/QP_ppa_chosex.F external_c/stack.c common/QP_state_table_setup.F pol_function/X_O_rotate.F pol_function/X_os.F interface/setup.F interface/.objects interface/init.F interface/barriers.F sc/SC_driver.F sc/V_exx.F io/io_SC_components.F modules/mod_BS.F modules/mod_drivers.F modules/std_presets.F modules/mod_D_lattice.F modules/mod_global_XC.F bse/K_driver.F bse/K_solvers.F bse/K_scattering_cpl.F bse/K.F driver/self.h

  Bugs:
  - Small bugs reported by Myrta.

  Additions:
  - Calculation of non collinear spin in spp [Fabrizio]
  - Self consistent local potentials + GS [Andrea, beta version]
  - Small changes in QP_ppa_chosex and QP_XX_Vxc to be called
    by SC_driver [Andrea]
  - inv_index is the index of the inversion symmetry.
    It is used instead of nsym/2+1 to do BS coupling
    even without time-reversal [Andrea]
  - barrier.F in interface. It will contain the barriers
    to specific runlevels, for example with n_spin=2 ACFDT
    total energy calculation are not implemented. [Andrea]
  - Added possibility to do TDHF in K.F (in the _SC project) [Andrea]
  - in _CPL project [Maurizia, beta version]

  Patch sent by: Andrea, Maurizia, Fabrizio & Myrta


