    and passed to setup. This is to syncronize Ken and Xen
    when Self-Consistent energies are used.
  - QP_ppa_chosex adapated to be called by SC_driver
  - Still changes in X_O_rotate (under development)
  - setup.F now calculates energies and occupation
    for all energy types (including SC corrections).
    QP corrections are, then, added in self_driver, K_driver ...

