    string in input file. the routine che either stop the job
    there or return a .true. value.

  Changes:
  - [SPP] collinear exciton spin calculation added.
  - Big update of SC project. Still unstable: local potential
    optics ok, wfs rotation implemented. Still to do non-local
    potentials.

