  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@203 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.0.13 r.202. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure spp/exc_properties.F spp/exc_wf_sort_and_report.F spp/exc_collinear_spin.F spp/mod_SPP.F spp/spp_i.F spp/exc_wf_eval.F spp/.objects spp/spp_init_load.F spp/spp_init.F include/version.inc config/configure.ac parser/mod_itm.F ChangeLog driver/spp.h

