  - spp/exc_collinear_spin.F [Fabrizio]

  Changes:
  - spp/exc_properties.F replaces spp/exc_wf_eval.F [Andrea]
  - spp -e now requires an option. 3 options are available
    now: s(ort), p(lot) and sp(in)
    When using with -e s not infile editing is done anymore, spp
    simply runs and report sorted energies and residuals [Andrea]

