  Bugs:
  - [X_os]: Half matrix now is calculated only when SPINV=.false. and
    at very low energy. Previous bounds induced small errors.

  Additions:
  - [mod_drivers, CHOSEX approximation (self -p c). Now PPA runs when called with
    (self -p p). Off-diagonal terms now availables in PPA also.
  - [mod_xc_functionals,7sc dir,init*] Self-Consistency driver and
    modules added for DFT potentials and (optionally) HF, CHOSEX, PPA
    SC calculations.
  - [QP_XX_Vxc,DFT_Vxc]: Off-diagonal terms added.
  - [mod_IO]: new logical read_dbs to switch off the IO reading.

  Changes:
  - [wf_load,fft_setup]: checks about loaded wf's changed.
    Replaced with a more careful test of FFT size and fft_g_table.
  - Old PJ_SC removed and replaced with PJ_DFT (now PJ_SC)

  Patch sent by: Andrea & Myrta


