  Changes:
  - [PJ_RAS] Real space cutoff in perpendicular direction implemented (for REELS use).
  - [PJ_RAS] Surface/slab dielectric functions with real space cutoff improved.

  Patch sent by: Conor


  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@170 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- Version 3.0.12. [Andrea Marini]

  *  configure spp/spp_i.F spp/exc_wf_eval.F include/version.inc config/configure.ac 0modules/mod_IO.F 0modules/mod_com.F 2io/ioBS.F 3qp_ctl/QP_apply_interpolate.F 6qp/QP_driver.F driver/spp.h driver/driver.c

  Bugs:
  - Wrong spin resolved indexes in QP_driver (thanks to Claudio).

  Additions:
  - in exc_wf_eval  now the distribution of the excitonic weight
    in the k-points is reportes.
  - Restored -I and -O options in spp.

  Changes:
  - In basic IO procedures existing files are searched in INPATH/SAVE and
    OUTPATH/SAVE-JOB folders (before was only in INPATH). This is to be able to read
    a BS kernel (for example) in the same run it was generated (with inpath/=outpath).
  - ioBS searches in SAVE if not found in JOB folder.

  Patch sent by: Andrea


