    the bug reported by D. Prezzi

  Changes:
  - [IMPORTANT]: p2s interfaces deeply revisited. Now using the configure
    it is possible to choose between an interface that uses : pw_export, qexml pw ver. 3.1
    or ver. 3.2
    *** New flag added to configure
        --with-p2s=<mode>       Interface mode in PW 2 SELF : <export> <3.1> <3.2>

