- V 3.0.9_11-05-07. [Andrea Marini]

  *  spp/k_analyze.F spp/spp_init.F spp/elph_pw_dbs.F 0modules/mod_electrons.F 2io/ioDB1.F 5X/X_pre_setup.F 5X/X_eh_setup.F 5X/X_os.F 5X/.objects 5X/X_Gf.F 5X/X_bare_RIM_Gf.F 5X/X_RIM_Gf.F 7bse/K_dump_to_o_file.F 7bse/K_diagonalization.F 7bse/K_inversion.F 7bse/K_solvers.F 4it/init_load.F 3qp_ctl/QP_apply_interpolate.F 3qp_ctl/mod_QP_CTL.F 3qp_ctl/QP_apply_stretch.F 3qp_ctl/QP_apply_fit.F 3qp_ctl/QP_apply_db.F 3qp_ctl/QP_apply_done.F 1common/extend_occupations.F 1common/run_summary.F 1common/coarse_grid.F 1common/fermi_level.F 5elph/ELPH_K_print.F

