  - src/1common/extend_occupations.F: Xe%E_RIM levels shift added twice, in this
    routine and in the Fermi routine.

  Additions:
  - src/5X/X_os.F: support for a calculation with QP Z's and widths (coarse_grid
    skipped). X_bare_RIM_Gf.F routine changed and renamed accordingly.
  -  src/7bse/K_inversion.F: support for a calculation with QP Z's and widths.

  Changes:
  - src/2io/ioDB1.F: %W and %Z are now allocated when QP corrections are added
  - mod_electrons.F (E_duplicate): when a level type is duplicated QP
    corrections are copied as well only if the destination type is empty (naive)
  - src/3qp_ctl/*.F: QP widths and Z's support enabled.
  - src/3qp_ctl/mod_QP_CTL.F: energy corrections on %E_RIM added.


  Patch sent by: Andrea


