- V 3.0.8_23-03-07. [Andrea Marini]

  *  3.0.8_16-03-07 include/version.inc p2s/p2s_qexml_db1.F p2s/p2s_db1.F 2wf_and_fft/el_density.F 2wf_and_fft/scatter_Bamp.F 0modules/mod_electrons.F 0modules/std_presets.F 0modules/mod_BS.F 0modules/mod_X.F 0modules/mod_ELPH.F 2io/ioDB1.F 2io/ioWF.F 2io/ioOSTNTS.F 2io/ioE_RIM.F 5X/X_O_longitudinal.F 5X/X_O_transverse.F 5X/X_os.F 5X/O_driver.F 5X/X_O_strengths.F 5X/X_O_gks.F 5X/X_s.F 7bse/Kernel_by_V.F 7bse/K_driver.F 7bse/K_eh_setup.F 7bse/K_solvers.F 4it/setup.F 4it/init.F 3qp_ctl/mod_QP_CTL.F 3qp_ctl/QP_apply_stretch.F 3qp_ctl/QP_apply_db.F 6qp/QP_secant.F 4ras/X_O_longitudinal_cut.F 1common/extend_occupations.F 1common/fermi_msg.F 1common/bracket.F 1common/secant.F 1common/fermi_level.F 3kop/bz_samp_indexes.F 5elph/QP_elph.F ChangeLog 3.0.8_23-03-07

