    occupations.
  - NON COLLINEAR SPIN SUPPORT included -> now all energies,
    occupations, ... are dimensioned using n_sp_pol (even when n_spinor=2).
    => Note the important change in scatter_Bamp.F <=
  - El-Ph lifetimes support.

  Changes:
  - Several subroutines restyled
  - bracket and secant are nor functions.
  - fermi_level routine algorithm rewritten and optimized.

  Patch sent by: Andrea


