  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/trunk@83 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

- V 3.0.5_11-01-07. [Andrea Marini]

  *  spp/elph_epsm1_load.F spp/elph_dV_2_gkkp.F spp/elph_pw_dbs.F a2s/a2s_db1.F 2io/ioX.F src/5X/X_os.F src/5X/X_drude.F src/4it/setup.F src/4it/init.F src/4it/gops.F src/1common/fermi_level.F

  Bugs:
  - As RL_v_comp_acc is calculated in k_lattice the call to
    gops gave wrong shells.
    The two calls have been exchanged in setup.F
  - Drude tail can be added ONLY when there is a metallic band.
    In metallic systems with few k-points there could not be
    a metallic band even if the character is metallic (Al 2x2x2)

  Patch sent by: Andrea


